commit.message:
Merge pull request #4 from jonashaag/patch-1

Requirements
Updated link to github code for list attributes
List attributes example on continents module
Added links to docs for form tabs and includes
Renamed suit form tabs according to new variable names

Added default=0 attribute for Country model order column
Since Country order is not handled in general list, but in
Continent inlines, we must set default value, in case country is
added out of inline, otherwise DB error will be thrown
Removed name from list_editable for ContinentAdmin
Sortables for changelist (ModelAdmin), tabular inlines and django-mptt added
Added correct Github link to tabs example
